    div(class="col-md-6 solutions-illustration d-none d-md-block")
      img(src="./images/image-solutions-nusanet-bandung.png")
    div(class="col-md-6 solutions-tagline")
      h2 What We provide for your internet connection
      p Trusted by thousands of satisfied clients in Indonesia and we are always innovating to provide the best solution for you
      div(class="row solutions-list")
        div(class="col-md-11 row")
          div(class="col-md-3 col-6")
            img(src="https://jkt.nusa.net.id/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/speed2.png")
            h5 Speed
            p Our fast internet is dedicated to your satisfaction, supported by the system and we are ready to provide a different experience.
          div(class="col-md-3 col-6")
            img(src="https://jkt.nusa.net.id/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/stable3.png")
            h5 Stable
            p Fast internet is not enough, connectivity is one of our priorities. With a redundant connection, it will minimize downtime.
          div(class="col-md-3 col-6")
            img(src="https://jkt.nusa.net.id/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/secure2.png")
            h5 Secure
            p We use the best DNS and email protection to provide additional protection against spam, fraud and phishing.
          div(class="col-md-3 col-6")
            img(src="https://jkt.nusa.net.id/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/support3.png")
            h5 Support
            p We have a Support team that can help you if you have problems with your internet connection, and 24/7 Helpdesk ready to help you.
  
